markups.originaltext: 脱离模板的答案-晋升机会promotion opportunity

If you loan someone money and they cannot pay you back like you had agreed, the relationship will become strained and even ruined. Other things that people don’t like to lend are expensive things like electronics or sentimental items like family heirlooms. If something happened to them while they were in the possession of someone else, they could be expensive or even impossible to repair.
